"title": "4020: life, of faith",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4020",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The way by which believers journey through this world and into the life to come. Jesus Christ himself is the way to life.</p>\n<h2>Life seen as travelling with God</h2>\n<h3>Walking with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1\">GEN 17:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:22\">GEN 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:24\">GEN 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9\">GEN 6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:15\">GEN 48:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:13\">PSA 56:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:15\">PSA 89:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:5\">MIC 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:12\">ZEC 10:12</a></p>\n<h3>Journeying from the old to the new</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:19\">ISA 43:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:8\">EXO 18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3-Isa40:5\">ISA 40:3–40:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:13\">MIC 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>God's guidance along the way</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21\">EXO 13:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20\">EXO 23:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:32-Deut1:33\">DEU 1:32–1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:2\">DEU 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:12\">NEH 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:19\">NEH 9:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:9\">PSA 25:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:17\">JER 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:25\">GAL 5:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's ways</h2>\n<h3>Walking in God's way</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:8\">ISA 35:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:19\">GEN 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:20\">EXO 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:5\">DEU 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:9\">DEU 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:10-Job23:12\">JOB 23:10–23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:2\">PSA 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:30\">PSA 18:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10\">2TI 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>God teaches believers his way</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:17\">ISA 48:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:23\">1SA 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:35-1Kgs8:36\">1KI 8:35–8:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:26-2Chr6:27\">2CH 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:8-Ps25:9\">PSA 25:8–25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:12\">PSA 25:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:11\">PSA 86:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:30\">PSA 119:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:23\">PRO 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:3\">ISA 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:20-Isa30:21\">ISA 30:20–30:21</a>PSA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:11\">16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:2\">PSA 23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:20\">PRO 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:16\">JER 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></p>\n<h3>Sinners refuse to follow God's way</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:6\">ISA 53:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:11\">ISA 56:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:16\">ACT 14:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>All other routes end in death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:12\">PRO 14:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:28\">DEU 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:29\">DEU 31:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:17\">JDG 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:22\">2KI 21:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:6\">PSA 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:10\">PRO 15:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:25\">PRO 16:25</a></p>\n<h3>Those who travel God's way are blessed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:18\">PRO 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:33\">DEU 5:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23\">1KI 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:5\">PRO 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:7-Isa26:8\">ISA 26:7–26:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3-Matt5:12\">MAT 5:3–5:12</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the way to life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:3\">COL 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a>ACT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:2\">9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:9\">ACT 19:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:23\">ACT 19:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:14\">ACT 24:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:22\">ACT 24:22</a></p>\n<h2>Entrance to the way to life</h2>\n<h3>Entrance is restricted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13-Matt7:14\">MAT 7:13–7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:9\">JHN 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a></p>\n<h3>Entrance is by faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:8-Heb11:10\">HEB 11:8–11:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:15-John3:16\">JHN 3:15–3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:7\">2CO 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:6\">HEB 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13-Heb11:16\">HEB 11:13–11:16</a></p>",
